		<content translate="true">Why Self-Regulation Matters</content>
	</text>
	<text id="nav_text" x="275" y="425" width="500" height="" autosize="H" style="PROMPT" visible="false" fx="PROMPT_SHOW" hidefx="PROMPT_HIDE">
		<content translate="true">Click a &lt;B&gt;Lesson&lt;/B&gt; or &lt;B&gt;Activity&lt;/B&gt; to learn more about &lt;B&gt;Why Self-Regulation Matters&lt;/B&gt;.</content>
	</text>
	<section id="presentation_text" align="LEFT" spacing="0x10" autospace="true" columns="0" exclusive="false" expanded="true">
		<text id="text01" x="25" y="50" width="300" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Self-regulation is a critical life skill.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text02" x="395" y="215" width="350" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">The better children are at self-regulating, the more successful they will be in school throughout childhood.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text03" x="75" y="395" width="350" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Children who learn to self-regulate are able to delay gratification and suppress their immediate impulses.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text04" x="400" y="395" width="350" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">The years between the ages of 3 and 5 appear to be when children begin to understand the relationship between their feelings and their behavior.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text05" x="400" y="395" width="350" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">Children who struggle with self-regulation, which is often independent of general intelligence, may face difficulty in transitioning to school.</content>
		</text>
		<text id="text06" x="400" y="395" width="350" height="" autosize="H" style="DEFAULT" visible="false" fx="TEXT_SHOW" hidefx="TEXT_HIDE">
			<content translate="true">&lt;B&gt;Key Message:&lt;/B&gt;&lt;LI&gt;Self-regulation develops gradually over the first years of life.&lt;/LI&gt;</content>
		</text>
	</section>
